text: James Campbell "Jamie" Irwin (16 April 1937 - 4 November 2005) was an Australian politician. He was a Liberal member of the South Australian Legislative Council from 1985 to 2002. From 1997 to 2002 he was President of the Council. ==References== Category:1937 births Category:2005 deaths Category:Liberal Party of Australia members of the Parliament of South Australia Category:Members of the South Australian Legislative Council Category:Presidents of the South Australian Legislative Council Category:Place of birth missing Category:20th-century Australian politicians Category:21st- century Australian politicians
